Text: Helemaal super! Ben ook erg benieuwd!!!

Not the best but definitely not the worst.  It seems like this may have been from the 3-D version.  Don't get me wrong if you must see it then you won't be upset, but if you're really looking for high quality this might not be the one for you.  Out of 5 stars I would give it a 3+.

Bedankt Pioen , Toppertje weer en gefeliciteerd met de top positie

Rocco
